House Warming
Dustin went
Fucking Julie beat me by one day. I got my new place all set up (only took me two months), and so now it's time to celebrate. There will be plenty of alcohol on hand. Also really good music. I've been making the playlist my whole life. So if you live in PA, remember that it's Saturday night and it's just a Caltrain ride away. You can take Caltrain to Milbrae, then BART to 24th street and it's a 5 minute walk from there. You can probably crash on my floor too. People in SF - it's right near 26th and Valencia. Ring the bell at 3603 or call my cell when you're here.
Saturday, December 6, 2008 at 9:00pm - Sunday, December 7, 2008 at 5:00am in PST
My New Place,3603 26th Street,San Francisco,California,United States
